node.text:
Available on February 1st exclusively at BAPE STORE® MIAMI and release on us.bape.com on February 8th. The first 100 customers who purchase a collaboration item at the Miami store will be eligible to attend the J Balvin meet and greet.
This will be a first come, first serve release. Store lineup will begin at 8 am EST and the store will be open at 9 am EST. Any customer that lineup before 8 am and/or do any overnight camping at the store will not be eligible to purchase ANY ITEM and will be asked to leave the vicinity. 
Customers who are eligible to meet J Balvin will receive a wristband that must be worn after receiving the wristband and will be asked to come back at a later time for the meet and greet. Customers with broken wristbands in any way will not be allowed to participate. 
@jbalvin  @miamidesigndistrict  @karizmavisuals  #bape #jbalvin
#miamidesigndistrict

node.text:
@bape_japan "A BATHING APE® STADIUM ROAD SHOP"

The "STADIUM ROAD SHOP" will feature a special BAPE® CAMO associated with the historic sports festival, along with graphics to enhance the event. In addition, the interior has been completely redesigned with an installation that mimics a stadium, giving the store a sporty and energetic finish. 
A number of special items created especially for this concept store and BAPE® archive items with a sporting taste will be available for purchase, providing a variety of contents for people to enjoy.

Address : 3-29-11 JINGUMAE SHIBUYA-KU TOKYO ZIP 150-0001 JAPAN
Phone : +81-3-5770-4455
Open : 11:00 ~ 20:00

この夏、開催されるスポーツの祭典を記念したコンセプトショップがオープンします。2021年7月22日(木)～9月5日(日)の間、BAPE KIDS® 原宿が全面リニューアルされ、期間限定の「STADIUM ROAD SHOP」として生まれ変わります。この「STADIUM ROAD SHOP」では、歴史的なスポーツの祭典にちなんだスペシャルなBAPE® CAMOが登場し、グラフィックとともにイベントを盛り上げます。さらに内装は一新され、スタジアムを模したインスタレーションを設置、店内はスポーティでエネルギッシュな仕上がりになっています。
また、このコンセプトショップのために作られた数々のスペシャルアイテムや、スポーツテイスト溢れるベイプ®のアーカイブアイテムも発売され、沢山の方々に楽しんで頂けるコンテンツをご用意しています

期間: 2021 年7 ⽉22 ⽇(木・祝)〜9 ⽉5 ⽇(日) 
〒150-0001　東京都渋谷区神宮前3-29-11 Tel: 03-5770-4455 
営業時間: 11:00 - 20:00 

#bape #abathingape
#bapestadiumroadshop
